{"tid":273762,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老味 搭巴士隔離個廢老有勁濃尿味","createTime":"2017-06-06T23:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T16:30:01.000Z","uid":9767,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac062cc38f737adb769812faf5537bca4f90a06b","tid":273762,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:24:28.000Z","msg":"懷疑超過兩星期無沖涼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n四周圍啲人咒撚晒眉頭 有啲就掩住個鼻<br />\n明顯佢地都聞到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但成車逼爆無得調位 <br />\n<br />\n好彩隔離個女仔有用香水 所以我聞到陣味無咁撚臭<br />\n但我一路打呢個post 見到佢個表情就係忍唔撚到笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8397e285ac9f3d917bc947cdca7875c55d8f5a65","tid":273762,"uid":54455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T23:32:51.000Z","msg":"嘩屌"},{"pid":"97d1c671003485797dff5a932fd854fcfd2e06d7","tid":273762,"uid":23592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:00:42.000Z","msg":"我都試過 我企正前面 仲要同時有兩個坐一前一後 佢哋落車後有個痴線佬即刻坐左其中一個個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98df2b0dc3dfd802bcd069ab2cbb10260ac0d631","tid":273762,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"下手坐落個位度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde778a6ed02111e16e11ead90f65261eb16039a","tid":273762,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:14:46.000Z","msg":"終於落車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f76f1eae674dd5261fbb66d3ec64606c866430","tid":273762,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T00:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac