"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過出於禮貌同尊重 無人出聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4b0e4bdd7a3236dfd8fce4443df340d716cfd8","tid":273762,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚有畫面隔住個Mon都聞到陣味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n巴打試過？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e9c4b94fa38e310d442841d0350bee4edb9ea9","tid":273762,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n滿人 走唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1a41913adf5c81e6ff0bebf7d19bec0370bfa7","tid":273762,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T01:39:17.000Z","msg":"諗起都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1eb5fc178151b06c9adad3da0bf22c5b05d8d21","tid":273762,"uid":106430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚有畫面隔住個Mon都聞到陣味呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n巴打試過？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港廢老咁撚多 試過1/2次咁大把 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a516963b5f07dba378c32bbf70bfdce3938bbcf0","tid":273762,"uid":8294,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"其實可以係尿袋"},{"pid":"78b1712a59ce02abe1fbdb